{"tid":2368841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人time capsule","createTime":"2021-01-16T14:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T14:57:02.000Z","uid":54622,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4269f847dad9aa5dc3350fe6d563030162d232","tid":2368841,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日同朋友行龍脊入鶴咀燈塔行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到個紅卜卜郵箱出現喺燈塔後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行埋去諗住影下見到啲寫左字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6qsGDT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6qsGDT.jpg&h=200d919c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PRrGL5x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPRrGL5x.jpg&h=b3f406ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面擺左兩部錄音機同幾餅錄音帶，我同朋友都錄左少少，當紀錄低喺咁痴撚線嘅一年嘅時刻.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位行開嗰邊hea嘅不妨玩下<br />\n<br />\n最後多謝擺機嘅有心人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d76049419df76789b8d1218efde2b43b56ac96","tid":2368841,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"20fc655f5449164fa25de72615685c13bf351e08","tid":2368841,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"fc005410e6c5bb41aba2ea81dc31d51d0fae8740","tid":2368841,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:28:10.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"8bb44abef0de012bbab138d8f4cad51339a6f73a","tid":2368841,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"d550d29c9306271bc4266bd3cacaa6b1bd5c8a6